'''海灣鐵路'''（{{lang-ar|سكة الحديد الخليجية}}）是計劃中連接[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]六個{{link-en|海灣合作委員會|Gulf Cooperation Council}}的鐵路線。全線總長2,177公里，預計耗資2500億美元建造<ref>{{cite web|title=EU, GCC to sign MoU on railway cooperation|url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1037771/saudi-arabia|website=Arab News|accessdate=10 February 2017|language=en|date=12 January 2017|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807170845/https://www.arabnews.com/node/1037771/saudi-arabia|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原计划在2023年完成<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bridge |first1=Sam |title=Kuwait said to start work on 111km railway project |url=https://www.arabianbusiness.com/transport/403177-kuwait-said-to-start-work-on-111km-railway-project |website=ArabianBusiness.com |accessdate=11 January 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801151430/https://www.arabianbusiness.com/transport/403177-kuwait-said-to-start-work-on-111km-railway-project |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

每個成員國都負責落實在本國境內的鐵路線部分，並會興建各自的鐵路線、支線、車站和貨運總站。費用會根據鐵路在各國長度比例分配。因此，阿聯酋和沙特阿拉伯將投資最多，之後分別是阿曼、卡塔爾、科威特和巴林。{{link-en|沙特鐵路公司|Saudi Railway Company}}將興建沙特阿拉伯的鐵路網，{{link-en|阿提哈德鐵路|Etihad Rail}}會建造阿聯酋鐵路網，{{link-en|阿曼鐵路|Oman Rail}}建造阿曼鐵路網，{{link-en|卡塔爾鐵路|Qatar Rail}}建造卡塔爾鐵路網<ref name="Railway Gazette1">{{cite web|last1=UK|first1=DVV Media|title=Gulf Railway could start next year|url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/gulf-railway-could-start-next-year.html|website=Railway Gazette|accessdate=10 February 2017|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807133647/https://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/gulf-railway-could-start-next-year.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

